Maybe it's balance rate,
maybe it's conversion rate,

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:31.174
maybe it's something else.

00:14:31.174 --> 00:14:32.840
Go ahead and run
performance experiments

00:14:32.840 --> 00:14:35.590
and see what the effects are.

00:14:35.590 --> 00:14:37.420
