Get your very important person
to see and to feel these things

00:15:45.105 --> 00:15:48.330
so that they actually
care about this stuff too.

00:15:48.330 --> 00:15:50.700
You want to get them to feel it.

00:15:50.700 --> 00:15:55.510
Once they understand you can
help them empower others.

00:15:55.510 --> 00:15:57.680
By changing how you're
very important people think

